name: Venus #1
description:
This is my new series of soundscape and ambient sound with collage and photography featuring Venus, the second planet on our solar system. 

Venus is also a name for roman goddess of beauty and love, This series i tried to combine photography, collage, graphics and also music to visualized in amidst of the chaos in our world, there's still beauty walking around us. 

Will be minted in very limited edition
